imdb.title: Dâti pea
imdb.plot: Kei and Yuri - The Dirty Pair aka 'The Lovely Angels' are two teen girls that fight crime throughout the universe and bring the bad guys to justice, but not before wrecking a planet.

episodes.title: Konpyuuta no koroshi kata oshiemasu
episodes.plot: A priceless prism is being delivered to Caine Galaxy. For safety, 20 different ships are being deployed, but only one of them has the actual gem. Kei and Yuri aren't sure if their cargo is real or not, but they must battle a group of pirates who intend to find out!

episodes.title: Kawaii tenshi wa munage ga osuki?
episodes.plot: Cosmo Plane Service has fallen victim to two suspicious accidents and now they're launching the Tenan I Spacecraft, their most expensive ship yet.

episodes.title: Katte ni bokera na! Koi wa roshian ruuretto
episodes.plot: King is the leader of a crime syndicate on Planet Vega. It's said he holds the Golem Poker Chip, which brings good luck to anyone who owns it. Kei and Yuri have been sent to infiltrate King's estate and bring that chip back into the hands of the law!

episodes.title: Tsuiseki wa chiizukeeki to shi no nioi
episodes.plot: The Guillaume De Malatesta XIII cat has run away! He was the test subject for a muscle fortifier that grants superhuman strength. If the Dirty Pair can't find him soon the city could be leveled flat!

episodes.title: Kiken ga ippai, damii ga ippai
episodes.plot: A priceless prism is being delivered to Caine Galaxy. For safety, 20 different ships are being deployed, but only one of them has the actual gem. Kei and Yuri aren't sure if their cargo is real or not, but they must battle a group of pirates who intend to find out!

episodes.title: Ai kososubete inochi kake masu tohiko!!
episodes.plot: Clicky is the sole heir to the wealthy Goldjeff empire. He's eloping with a woman named Joanca, but she has plans to kidnap him and walk away with millions of credits in ransom money. It's up to the Dirty Pair to step in and set things right!

episodes.title: Yarukkyaanai! koha onna no kibakuzai
episodes.plot: Yuri received a shocking message from Billy Galet. Billy was Yuri's childhood sweetheart who promised to build her a spaceship. Now Yuri wants to retire and fly off with Billy, but Kei won't give up so easily.

episodes.title: Uchirawo katte! yojinbo niha bijin gao e
episodes.plot: Newstone Ore is a highly sought-after source of fuel, but fighting between two rival syndicates has lead to a drop in the supply. The Dirty Pair are sent in disguised as the feisty Shooting Star Okei and the beautiful sharpshooter Crimson Oyuri!

episodes.title: E tsutsutsu? uchiraga kyoaku yukaihan!
episodes.plot: The beloved King Louis VII, ruler of Planet Caspia, has died. If anything happens to his only son, Prince Heace, the throne will go to the villainous Duke Ruber. The Queen has called in the Dirty Pair to bring the prince home safely.

episodes.title: Hohoho, doresu to otoko wa onyû ni kagiru
episodes.plot: Kei and Yuri have received a dinner invitation from the handsome G.A. Frances. But when they stop by Planet Cauld for a little pre-dinner dress shopping, the police aren't too happy to see them.

episodes.title: Chiisa na dokusaisha! fura nu kimitsu nitatarinashi
episodes.plot: Algernon has been stolen! The thief is in the 3WA building and the Dirty Pair are called to smoke him out, but no one will tell them what exactly was stolen, or who stole it. How can they find something if they don't know what they're looking for?

episodes.title: Nani yokore! tama noo hada ga dorondoron
episodes.plot: Something lurking in the sewers is eating Eleanor City residents. Much to the chagrin of the Tower Chief, the Dirty Pair are back to save the day.

episodes.title: Kinko ka senkyo ka? enzetsu aha satsujin biyori
episodes.plot: Security is tight at 3WA Headquarters, for two reasons: Presidential Candidate Guilder is there for a speech, and maintenance is underway on Pandora's Vault. But a shadowy figure sneaks in and the Dirty Pair must find out if he is he after Guilder or Pandora.

episodes.title: Kokohore nyannyan kahou wa saigo ni yattekuru
episodes.plot: An old coot by the name of Joe says he's on the trail of an enormous treasure! Catch is, it's in the deepest, darkest part of the ruins.

episodes.title: Makasenasai! WWWA ha suteki nao shigoto
episodes.plot: Sakurako Yorozuya may look like an ordinary young woman, but she's actually the head of a giant corporation! Kei and Yuri have been assigned to protect her, but babysitting this naive, high-society princess turns out to be a royal pain in the rear.

episodes.title: Dete koi dete koi ansatsu mono
episodes.plot: Sundric, a brilliant cryptanalyst and deadly assassin, has eluded the 3WA for thirteen years, but they have one last chance to catch him. The Dirty Pair go undercover as Flight Attendant Yuri and Sister Kei to smoke him out!

episodes.title: Yattane! dete kita 463 nin
episodes.plot: The mystery of Flight 807 continues, and it just keeps getting stranger. There are two ransom notes now, and Arthur is adamant that the newest one is a fake! But how would a child know something like that? What's more, the kidnappers are asking for something called "File-E." Though the Dirty Pair is stumped, Eddie knows exactly what that is... but he's not telling. If Kei and Yuri are going to save the passengers of Flight 807, they'll have to figure out Eddie's secrets first!

episodes.title: Fuan dawa...!? uchirano karei naru hofuku
episodes.plot: A devious dealer named Mahogany has almost finished manufacturing a terrible new drug. Kei and Yuri are ready to blow his entire operation away, but the 3WA won't let them. That's when Yuri meets a handsome, mysterious man who claims he can help them stop Mahogany.

episodes.title: Kanari maji? manshon ha kiken na adoresu
episodes.plot: The number of murders in the "Salesman Serial Killer Case" is at 32 and climbing. The Dirty Pair should be on the trail of the killer, but instead Gooley has them holed up in a condo, under strict orders not to leave. What could he be thinking?

episodes.title: Hieetsu! Yokan no boya ha tamineta!
episodes.plot: Garou used to be a brilliant engineer, but then he started making counterfeit money. His fakes are so convincing that the city has fallen into a financial crisis! The Dirty Pair are now following his tracks.

episodes.title: Ho, honki!? Bijo ni kyanon ho ha dasshutsu no kiwado
episodes.plot: Marcus, Security Captain for the Weapons Research Lab, has gone mad. He killed all the scientists and is holding Chief Gooley prisoner. This job is too big for the Dirty Pair and they're told to stay away. But Kei and Yuri can't just leave Gooley to die!
